Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:41.29,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いつか君と見上げた空は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.93,0:00:52.95,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}心の中　そっと溶けていく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:01:05.30,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}白いノートに書いた手紙は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.21,0:01:17.14,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}行く先を告げないまま閉じ込めた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.14,0:01:27.93,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}言葉にすれば戻れないから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.67,0:01:42.59,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いつも君と見上げた空は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:58.24,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}悲しいくらい青く  透きとおっていた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:41.29,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}曾几何时与你一起仰望过的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.93,0:00:52.95,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}渐渐溶入了心中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:01:05.30,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}白色的笔记本上写的信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.21,0:01:17.14,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}还未说明用意就匆匆合上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.14,0:01:27.93,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}因为话语总是覆水难收
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.67,0:01:42.59,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}总与你一同仰望的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:58.24,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}蔚蓝清澈得令人悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:57.72,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}スローモーション　蘇る校舎の影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:22:05.54,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夕陽を浴びながら　私たちは笑ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:16.79,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}お互いあの時から変わってない身長なんだけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.79,0:22:23.54,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}見える景色　変わったかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.54,0:22:27.89,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同じポケットじゃないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.89,0:22:32.14,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同じ宝物が眠る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.14,0:22:36.49,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}喜び悲しみ全部share!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.49,0:22:41.10,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}分け合って泣いて笑ったね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.10,0:22:49.77,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一緒だよ　違った道の上でも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:57.72,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}慢镜回放校舍的影子中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:22:05.54,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}沐浴着夕阳的我们在欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:16.79,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我们从那时起虽然身高都没变化
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.79,0:22:23.54,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}可是看到的风景却变了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.54,0:22:27.89,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}虽然各自拥有不同的口袋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.89,0:22:32.14,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}可里边却睡着同样的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.14,0:22:36.49,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}欢乐和悲伤全都share!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.49,0:22:41.10,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}分享着我们的眼泪与笑声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.10,0:22:49.77,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}永远在一起  就算走在不同的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.13,0:00:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.47,0:00:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.23,0:00:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把风间...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.09,0:02:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 今天还去你家开作战会议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了是复习备考了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.43,0:02:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下校门见哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.31,0:02:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别迟到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.55,0:02:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的台词...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.18,0:02:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的点心是什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐 村雨同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨同学啊 最近和那两个人走得很近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.24,0:02:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...莲贺和当麻?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.02,0:02:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来啊...那两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是在交往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀! 问出来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.88,0:02:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊 是不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种问题 是不是应该问当事人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是同班同学 没必要太客气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:03:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到自己的名字当然会回来的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即然这样那就问个清楚好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个在交往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.26,0:03:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们总是在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且给人的感觉也很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然一部分男生狂热地支持你们...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.07,0:03:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话我们看你们都觉得有点不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样还说没有交往的话就太假了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 两个女生在一起都做些什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.92,0:03:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为满足好奇心而窥测他人的自我同一性之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.92,0:03:27.67,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}(自我同一性 是指青少年的需要、情感、能力、目标\N价值观等特质整合为统一的人格框架)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说我没有向你们说明什么的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位难道说爱一个人还要在意他的性别吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.26,0:03:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在意...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们真的在交往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合? 真正的百合?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.36,0:03:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 嘛 这就是个人的爱好问题了...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事 不是该在教室里大声谈论的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.89,0:03:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊 苍井 怎么这么败兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.16,0:03:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨同学你也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?我?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为班级委员居然带头谈论
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...不要脸的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶? 没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人不愉快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然说人不要脸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干...干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.47,0:04:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想用暴力威胁我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是朋绘!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能若无其事地做这种别人不敢做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人过电 我的偶像!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀...你该生气才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 所谓的不要脸最起码也得是这样...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:04:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍井同学...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会嘴上逞能啊 最近的年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.34,0:05:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和她同岁吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.31,0:05:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...这么说来没有告诉你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋绘休学过两年 今年已经十八岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.36,0:05:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶——?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶? 为...为什么以前不说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.08,0:05:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们没问啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是该去追下苍井同学?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被弄脏了...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅我吧 真纱香姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓 没有爱的亲吻不作数哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就当做是被狗咬了忘掉它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.99,0:06:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是两个人互相思念的心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对就像你对我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有它在 你就不会被弄脏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对梓来说真纱香姐姐大人就是唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作者是...织野...真纱香啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说还不是很畅销
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过很好看的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.19,0:06:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用古风文体描写女孩子之间的友情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.74,0:06:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然作者的个人信息完全没有公开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是个又美丽又浪漫的大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 苍井同学...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织野真纱香是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风间她老哥的笔名...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:06.47,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}(风间老哥的名字是风间范夫かざまのりお\N倒过来就是おりのまさか织野真纱香)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为作品就是作者的投影
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱着包括真纱香姐姐在内的这整个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这样 是没法告诉她真相了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那是她莹润的唇发出的一声叹息」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不 也许是一篇小诗也说不定」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是拿了新人奖的那个短篇的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这你都知道啊 都还没有出单行本呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的啊 不过真的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.58,0:07:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道的啊 村雨同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很deep地 很core地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛...嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.48,0:07:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 要惹火上身...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 我周围没有喜欢这位作家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:08:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还担心是不是真的没人气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你是姐姐大人的粉丝应该明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.89,0:08:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像莲贺同学她们那样光明正大地...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得什么地方有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.28,0:08:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛...确实 那样是有点...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也这么想?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们很合得来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子之间的爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该发生在更隐秘的地方...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更纯洁 更梦幻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得正因为这样才美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 比如这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后 在校舍的一角
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.73,0:08:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远处传来学生们的喧嚣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又好像海浪的声音一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.31,0:08:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后渐渐地消融在风里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只留下...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相视的两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:08:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OUT!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:08:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SAFE!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.91,0:09:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是的 太没教养了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过太好了 居然同班里就有能理解我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们看来能成为好朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲贺的事 你就别怪她了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也不是什么坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了 托风间同学的福我已经好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.58,0:09:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回教室去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.63,0:09:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.21,0:09:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风 风间...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...那 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 风间!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 苍井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.70,0:10:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风间 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.33,0:10:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是滑了下 摔倒了而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就是啊 所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.26,0:10:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 为什么 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风间...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.69,0:10:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到哪去了啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教室里吵起来了大事不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是班级委员吗 想想办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:10:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:02.21,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 现在我...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:03.92,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 快点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱宫君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫那个?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把风间...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:20.44,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}(从左到右 小贺 大妈 小莲 莲桑 莲贺前辈)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.02,0:11:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了叫法吵起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.48,0:11:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨同学觉得哪个好?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小!莲!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个倒也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.81,0:11:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊...村雨同学...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 为什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风间为什么哭了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.02,0:12:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我...为什么风间会...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛嘛 欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.89,0:12:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本打算开始第十二次女子部设立作战会议的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 不是复习备考吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个等会议结束再说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.48,0:12:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小汐? 喂喂?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不通!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.39,0:12:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要哭呢 那种情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.88,0:13:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦啊啦 好热闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.93,0:13:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.06,0:13:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风间君 村雨君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.78,0:13:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我手滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.91,0:13:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你大两岁就...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不知道发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个是不是有必要单独谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.76,0:13:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来大两岁也不是白大的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到回家以前应该就干了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉 干衣机正好坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.43,0:14:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 道场那边倒是有用来烘干道服的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不过你看 今天天气这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.03,0:14:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晾在竹竿上好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那眼泪又是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.42,0:14:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 女人心真是搞不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯不行啊 用那么大力气会洗皱的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯真是做不来这种事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学习又好 运动又好 空手道也那么厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像男孩子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.03,0:14:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定是因为这个才哭的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推倒苍井同学的小纯 就像粗暴的男孩子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粗暴的...男孩子?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太没品了 居然想靠力气征服女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太好了 松了口气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我苦恼了好久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.34,0:15:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粗暴的...男孩子...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会那么做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.48,0:15:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯不会做那种事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了你以外 对谁都不会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起~~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也弄洒了~~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.84,0:16:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.35,0:16:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她看上去好像在等那一句话一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 我可以有所期待吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.03,0:16:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏在风间心里的...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我的感情...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也够热的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.17,0:16:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话也许比干衣机还要干得快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.13,0:16:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.58,0:16:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了小纯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.63,0:16:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和苍井同学都聊了点什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.26,0:16:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.97,0:16:49.72,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂~村雨同学~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.81,0:16:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我做的 织野真纱香姐姐大人的...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.18,0:16:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉丝会报
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:17:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织野...真纱香...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:04.29,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(日语 不会吧=まさか 和真纱香同音)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为...为什么你们也在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.54,0:17:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.44,0:17:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 少女小说家的同人志啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且好像执笔者只有你一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.43,0:17:29.00,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这一句中就能管窥姐姐大人热情的火焰...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.84,0:17:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...可以回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:30.46,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要大声读出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:32.17,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有色情的吗 色情的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:35.14,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说有色情的吗 色情的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真热闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:35.84,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说有点自我陶醉的嫌疑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.74,0:17:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过字里行间弥漫着你对那位作家的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的充满热情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:18:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学校时对你的无礼 希望你能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.75,0:18:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很有天份的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.08,0:18:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要加入女子部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.14,0:18:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然喜欢女孩子就应该加入我们女子部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...其实...没有那种爱好...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只喜欢真纱香姐姐大人编制的细腻世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.86,0:18:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别拿来和你们那种现实主义的感情相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.97,0:18:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 村雨同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈...怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.07,0:18:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你~难~道~是~傻~瓜~吗~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种死脑筋的大脑门 只会惹人烦而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.41,0:18:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大脑门!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.77,0:18:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这么说来以前你们不是也找过我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.67,0:18:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.24,0:18:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊! 已经四点了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.42,0:18:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该复习了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:18:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就要学习了啊 烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 没能好好招待你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 我才是 突然登门造访
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.36,0:19:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书送你了 请你读一读
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.87,0:19:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话告诉我感想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.45,0:19:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 各位 晚饭想吃什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:19:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经这个时间了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃肉 吃肉~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.00,0:20:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太没教养了哦 你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这样你们真打算在这吃了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也不是不可以...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服洗好后就给你拿回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不用洗的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我得给哥哥做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.06,0:20:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 小纯 我要来还不是随时能来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.53,0:20:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.22,0:20:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个 你哥哥应该想读读的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.49,0:20:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍井同学还放下了很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.12,0:20:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他读完你再拿来也行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.13,0:20:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:20:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.93,0:20:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.71,0:21:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.36,0:21:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.85,0:21:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯真是的 这样我不是走不了了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.24,0:21:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BYEBYE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.46,0:23:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这个女孩子哦 她把这书送到编辑部了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.50,0:23:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.31,0:23:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你读同一所学校的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.18,0:23:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥的那个织野真纱香 小心别暴露了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.19,0:23:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光听你这句话 还以为我有多红呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.95,0:23:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实根本就不红呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.24,0:23:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.32,0:23:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哇 噢~...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.16,0:23:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是这个意思...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.60,0:23:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢~...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.26,0:23:52.28,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一话 [你是向日葵]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.68,0:23:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.02,0:23:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧...

